#Stinnett, Mark -[Mid-term] 2019-10-28
print("Planet Express Delivery Time Calculator")

planetpersei=input("What is the name of the planet?")
parsecs1=input("How many parsecs away?")
numberofpackages=input("How many packages?")
packagesweight=input("How many tons does each package weigh?")

#operations
parsecs1=float(parsecs1)
numberofpackages=float(numberofpackages)

packagesweight=float(packagesweight)
totalcargoweight=(numberofpackages * packagesweight)


triptime=(totalcargoweight + parsecs1 * numberofpackages)
triptoearth=(parsecs1)
totaltriptime=(triptime + parsecs1)

print("The total cargo weight is",totalcargoweight,"ton(s).")
print("The trip to", planetpersei,"will take",triptime,"minutes.")
print("The trip back to earth will take",triptoearth,"minutes.")
print("The total trip time is",totaltriptime,"minutes.")
